### AI Report HTTP 测试用例
### 作者: liangjun
### 日期: 2025-10-14


### 1. 聊天测试 - 自我介绍
GET http://localhost:8080/ai/chat?message=请介绍一下你自己
Accept: text/plain

###

### 2. 知识库查询 - 查询销售额相关问题
GET http://localhost:8080/knowledge/search?question=如何计算销售额&topK=3
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. RAG 问答 - 查询销售额计算方法
GET http://localhost:8080/rag/chat?question=如何计算各部门的销售额？&topK=3
Accept: text/plain
###

### 4. NL2SQL - 查询各部门销售额
GET http://localhost:8080/rag/nl2sql?question=查询各部门的销售额&topK=3
Accept: text/plain

###

### 5. NL2SQL - 查询环比数据
GET http://localhost:8080/rag/nl2sql?question=查询各部门的月度环比销售额&topK=3
Accept: text/plain

###

### 6. 数据查询 - 各部门销售额
GET http://localhost:8080/report/query?question=查询各部门的销售额&topK=3
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. 数据查询 - 每月销售趋势
GET http://localhost:8080/report/query?question=查询每月的销售趋势&topK=3
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. 完整报告生成 - 部门销售分析（含 Word）
POST http://localhost:8080/report/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "question": "查询各部门的销售额",
  "topK": 3,
  "generateChart": true,
  "chartType": "bar",
  "generateWord": true
}

###

